OL,3,CThousands protest over mass tourism in
OL,4,CSpain's Canary Islands
OL,6,FThousands of protesters have taken
OL,7,Fpart in demonstrations against mass
OL,8,Ftourism in Spain's .
OL,10,FThe archipelago, which includes
OL,11,FTenerife, Fuerteventura and Gran
OL,12,FCanaria, is a popular destination for
OL,13,FBritish tourists, but the islands are
OL,14,Fstruggling to cope with the influx of
OL,15,Fvisitors.
OL,17,Fin 2023 around 14 million foreigners
OL,18,Fvisited the islands in the Atlantic
OL,19,Fwhich have a population of just 2.2
OL,20,Fmillion.
