OL,3,CThousands protest over mass tourism in
OL,4,CSpain's Canary Islands
OL,6,FDespite decades of mass tourism, the
OL,7,FCanary Islands remain poor compared to
OL,8,Fother regions of Spain and the average
OL,9,Fsalary of workers is one of the lowest
OL,10,Fin the country.
OL,12,FResidents living in the holiday
OL,13,Fdestination say too much tourism is
OL,14,Fdamaging the environment, driving down
OL,15,Fwages and squeezing locals out of the
OL,16,Fhousing market.
OL,18,FSome local people say they have been
OL,19,Fforced to sleep in their cars or even
OL,20,Fin caves.
